<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="id">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title><%= title %> - Unand Volunteer Hub</title>
    <link href="/css/tailwind.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        body { font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; }
        .accordion-content {
            max-height: 0;
            overflow: hidden;
            transition: max-height 0.3s ease-out;
        }
        .chevron {
            transition: transform 0.3s ease-out;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body class="bg-gray-50">
    <div class="flex h-screen">
        
        <%- include('../partials/sidebar_mahasiswa', { user: user, title: title }) %>

        <main class="flex-1 p-8 overflow-y-auto">
            <div class="flex justify-between items-center mb-8">
                <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-800">Frequently Asked Question</h1>
                <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-gray-200"></div>
            </div>

            <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-lg shadow-sm">
                <div class="text-center mb-10"><h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-800">Frequently Asked Question</h1><p class="text-gray-500 mt-2">(Pertanyaan yang Sering Diajukan)</p></div>
                <div class="space-y-4" id="accordion-container">
                    <div class="accordion-item border-b border-gray-200 pb-4"><button class="accordion-header w-full flex justify-between items-center text-left text-lg font-medium text-gray-800 py-2 focus:outline-none"><span>Bagaimana cara mendaftar sebagai volunteer?</span><svg class="chevron w-5 h-5 text-gray-500" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"></path></svg></button><div class="accordion-content"><p class="pt-2 text-gray-600">Anda dapat mendaftar melalui menu "Program Volunteer", pilih program yang diminati, lalu klik tombol "Daftar". Pastikan Anda telah melengkapi data profil Anda terlebih dahulu sebelum mendaftar.</p></div></div>
                    <div class="accordion-item border-b border-gray-200 pb-4"><button class="accordion-header w-full flex justify-between items-center text-left text-lg font-medium text-gray-800 py-2 focus:outline-none"><span>Apa saja persyaratan umum untuk menjadi volunteer?</span><svg class="chevron w-5 h-5 text-gray-500" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"></path></svg></button><div class="accordion-content"><p class="pt-2 text-gray-600">Persyaratan umum biasanya meliputi status sebagai mahasiswa aktif, memiliki komitmen tinggi, dan bersedia mengikuti semua rangkaian kegiatan. Persyaratan khusus akan dijelaskan pada detail masing-masing program.</p></div></div>
                    <div class="accordion-item border-b border-gray-200 pb-4"><button class="accordion-header w-full flex justify-between items-center text-left text-lg font-medium text-gray-800 py-2 focus:outline-none"><span>Apakah ada batas waktu pendaftaran?</span><svg class="chevron w-5 h-5 text-gray-500" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"></path></svg></button><div class="accordion-content"><p class="pt-2 text-gray-600">Ya, setiap program memiliki batas waktu pendaftaran yang berbeda-beda. Anda bisa melihatnya pada halaman detail program volunteer. Jangan sampai terlewat!</p></div></div>
                    <div class="accordion-item border-b border-gray-200 pb-4"><button class="accordion-header w-full flex justify-between items-center text-left text-lg font-medium text-gray-800 py-2 focus:outline-none"><span>Apakah saya bisa mengikuti lebih dari satu program volunteer sekaligus?</span><svg class="chevron w-5 h-5 text-gray-500" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"></path></svg></button><div class="accordion-content"><p class="pt-2 text-gray-600">Tergantung pada kebijakan masing-masing program. Beberapa program mungkin tidak memperbolehkan partisipasi ganda untuk memastikan fokus dan komitmen volunteer. Informasi ini biasanya tertera pada detail program.</p></div></div>
                    <div class="accordion-item"><button class="accordion-header w-full flex justify-between items-center text-left text-lg font-medium text-gray-800 py-2 focus:outline-none"><span>Bagaimana saya mengetahui status aplikasi pendaftaran saya?</span><svg class="chevron w-5 h-5 text-gray-500" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"></path></svg></button><div class="accordion-content"><p class="pt-2 text-gray-600">Status aplikasi Anda (diterima, ditolak, atau dalam proses seleksi) dapat dilihat pada menu "Riwayat Keikutsertaan". Anda juga akan menerima notifikasi melalui email yang terdaftar.</p></div></div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </main>
    </div>

    <script>
        document.querySelectorAll('.accordion-header').forEach(header => {
            header.addEventListener('click', () => {
                const content = header.nextElementSibling;
                const chevron = header.querySelector('.chevron');

                if (content.style.maxHeight) {
                    content.style.maxHeight = null;
                    chevron.style.transform = 'rotate(0deg)';
                } else {
                    content.style.maxHeight = content.scrollHeight + 'px';
                    chevron.style.transform = 'rotate(180deg)';
                }
            });
        });
    </script>
</body>
</html>
